Story_Texts.SourceString: The silhouette of a gothic castle pierces the horizon.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: The silhouette of a gothic castle pierces the horizon.

Story_Texts.SourceString: Swarms of flying Chiroptera-like rodents fill the sky overhead.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Swarms of flying Chiroptera-like rodents fill the sky overhead.

Story_Texts.SourceString: As they approach the gates, your heroes debate the nature of their enemy.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: As they approach the gates, your heroes debate the nature of their enemy.

Story_Texts.SourceString: Whatever it is, everyone except Razor agrees it is definitely not a vampire.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Whatever it is, everyone except Razor agrees it is definitely not a vampire.
